attributes.description:
Demo Dashboard for Quant Azimuth technical task.
provides statistics for archives:
• failed
• processed
• processed per second
• processed per minute
• remaining
for files:
• pie chart for indexed documents types
• vertical bar for indexed documents types
• separate counter of documents for each document type
• timeline
